strange wilderness is a 2008 comedy-adventure film produced by adam sandler 's production company , happy madison productions for paramount pictures , and starring steve zahn , allen covert , justin long , kevin heffernan , and jonah hill . the film received negative reviews and was a box office bomb , making less than $ 7 million against a $ 20 million budget . so far , this is the final happy madison productions film to be released by paramount pictures ( the ridiculous 6 was originally planned to be a paramount pictures film , but they rejected it ) . the logo for paramount pictures also does n't appear at the beginning , due to the movie 's poor reception .